title: 50 Cent Interview and More
itunes:title: 50 Cent Interview and More
description:
Wednesday 9/27- Today on the show our good friend and the King of shade 50 cent came by where he spoke about his new show 50 Central on BET, Power and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Ray Lewis after he said he was praying and not kneeling during the National Anthem this past weekend. Moreover, Angela gave advice to some listeners during "Ask Yee".
